00:28:08,040 --> 00:28:12,640 
She saved me the bother by
doing my job. My hand was hurting.

258
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:17,440 
She's a girl or l'd have
crushed her like an ant!

259
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:21,040 
Let's go.

