263
00:28:38,560 --> 00:28:40,040 
Don't you know?

264
00:28:41,080 --> 00:28:43,040 
You butt out.
Who asked you?

265
00:28:46,080 --> 00:28:50,080 
''- what the..? - You were
looking, my tummy will hurt.''

266
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,760 
Give me one.

267
00:28:56,080 --> 00:28:58,760 
''She will regret it..''

268
00:28:59,080 --> 00:29:01,080 
- You be quiet.
