l'll get there right away!

1128
01:51:34,240 --> 01:51:35,720 
My daughter has been found!

1129
01:51:40,400 --> 01:51:43,240 
Get the car ready fast.
l have found my daughter!

1130
01:51:43,720 --> 01:51:46,720 
l'll leave now.
Get ready fast.

1131
01:52:25,760 --> 01:52:27,160 
