Pay me 1000 bucks. lsn't it?

1191
01:57:43,680 --> 01:57:46,360 
Are you nuts?
Look at the poor chaps' face

1192
01:57:47,720 --> 01:57:50,680 
''Okay, l won't take money.
We forgive you.''

1193
